          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0664P0-10340'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0664P0_20040916_GCR_367' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        A designated individual should secure that suitable practices are used, but it does not have to be through a direct line management of every person involved in the activities. It is not clear that the adding of supervision would help in any way whatever in dealing with the issues I outlined previously. If the noble Baroness wishes to talk to me after she has read <span class="italic">Hansard,</span> I shall be happy to meet her.
      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0664P0-10341'>
        <a name='S5LV0664P0_20040916_GCR_368'>  </a>
