        Clause 18 [<span class="italic">Duty of the designated individual</span>]:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0664P0-10345'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0664P0_20040916_GCR_372' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
